Resource Profile: Bundle - ePI

Official URL: http://hl7.eu/fhir/ig/gravitate-health/StructureDefinition/Bundle-uv-epi Version: 0.1.0
Active as of 2022-04-20 Computable Name: BundleUvEpi

This profile represents the constraints applied to the Bundle resource by the Electronic Product Information (ePI) FHIR Implementation Guide.

An electronic product information (ePI) is authorised, statutory product information for medicines (i.e. summary of product characteristics, package leaflet and labelling) in a semi-structured format created using the common EU electronic standard.

Usage:

  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
